{"tid":1115073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夜店主動剝衫怪人映相 12萬人看過她狂歡裸胸　","createTime":"2019-04-19T02:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T02:36:40.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dcce58dccf42512907f8e914898a6847651300d1","tid":1115073,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"女生出門在外真的要懂得自保！英國一名女大生就表示，近日她到希臘札金索斯州(Zante)參加夜店狂歡，一時玩得太嗨，當場把衣服脫光，胸部無所遁形。但她回家後，發現早已有超過12萬人看過她的露奶影片，讓她非常生氣。<br />\n據英國《每日星報》報導，這名24歲匿名女大生說，當時她和朋友在夜店裡狂歡，現場氣氛相當嗨，於是衣服一件又脫掉一件，最後脫到只剩內褲。但女大生回家後，卻看到她的狂歡影像外流，她氣憤地說：「我真的不敢相信，他們未經我同意拍攝，甚至流出影像。」女大生說，現場她看到不少人正在拍攝，但不知道最後影片會這樣曝光，她也很擔心以後自己會被認出來，甚至導致求職路困難重重。她更直呼，這是她這輩子最恥辱的一刻。<br />\n現在歐美不少大學生，流行出國參加夜店狂歡趴，例如西班牙惡名昭彰的「性愛天堂」馬加洛夫(Magaluf)，就是英國人最愛到訪的地點之一。2014年就發生過一名18歲女子為了兌換雞尾酒，一口氣對24名男子口交。還有另一名18歲英國女子為了慶祝成年禮，在馬加洛夫的酒吧內任由15男子恣意猥褻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190419/640_50145e345bf94109aeb7c270af711c06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190419%2F640_50145e345bf94109aeb7c270af711c06.jpg&h=1c6a01e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190419/640_a0c45b5474ed1babbe4134b289baebd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190419%2F640_a0c45b5474ed1babbe4134b289baebd1.jpg&h=f0391147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190419/1553180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190419%2F1553180&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=08e9a856\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190419%2F1553180&h=5adf7df4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190419/1553180</a><br />\n<br />\n全是別人錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bc67b36daebc68771b5a9611d37da1e415e8a1","tid":1115073,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"6462b30884a4ffafe96b1dd95267f030d0d1e0b4","tid":1115073,"uid":36670,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"你有一分鐘救你阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963e2d58effd2d67bbd335e016ae73d117259677","tid":1115073,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"eafcc7835c604983e3c12f3eb43f06bd5bfc83f0","tid":1115073,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"29c1d7e4207002b25b19c277a50d88856e3a4caf","tid":1115073,"uid":94167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:23:45.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"aef26b6159e71e23b62d8c527a0c0a45ec549e3a","tid":1115073,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:34:02.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"723bd2e9ad63d16f628fdd73cac397ecf276a66a","tid":1115073,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b0135ace09250819c9b301eb47456e3041df1645","tid":1115073,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:36:40.000Z","msg":"Reddit trashyboner sub 睇到你唔想睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}